title: Nick Phoenix - Speed of Sound - flac
description:
Two Steps From Hell composer, Nick Phoenix has often taken the epic Two Steps genre into the electronica realm. Popular tracks like "Am I Not Human", "Our Last Hope" and "Titan Dream" will give you an idea of where "Speed Of Sound" is heading. There are some very strong melodies on this album and a cohesive theme that is very interesting and very Sci-Fi. Vocals on the album come from Aya Peard and Nick Phoenix. Percussion played by Greg Ellis, Satnam Ramgotra, Nick Phoenix, Toss Panos, Curt Bisquera and Peter Franken. Orchestra is Capellen Orchestra.

View my profile for the 320 kbps mp3 version.
